  }
}</pre></div>
<p dir="auto">This last json config way passes the <code>preset</code> object to the <code>conventional-changelog-preset-loader</code> package, that in turn, passes this same <code>preset</code> object as the config for the <code>conventional-changelog-conventionalcommits</code>.</p>
<p dir="auto">See <a href="https://github.com/conventional-changelog/conventional-changelog-config-spec">conventional-changelog-config-spec</a> for available configuration options.</p>
